          <h2>Welcome to Mental Constructs </h2>
          <p>Man has the ability to think. That is why you are not a monkey. You can think.</p>
          <p>Most of the times your mental-construct is lost. Here you can record them and organize them. Exhibit your Mental Constructs to others for judgements, ideas and of course, for General Consent (Don't worry, we all do it).</p>

          <p>We are all God's disciples, we exist so that our soul can attain enlightenment through experience. Experience builds thinking capacity, which a man can use to understand about life, the universe and everything (42, right?). There is so much in this world you do not know and there is so much in this world you cannot understand (women!!!).
