            <h3>Create and Organize Your Creative Constructs</h3>
            <p>This is not a Diary! Ideas and thoughts materialize but are never recorded by us. Here you can write entire constructs in a powerful editor and store them. Any Creative Constructs or thoughts can be stored indefinitely. Never lose your thoughts again. When thoughts become too many, you can organize them proficiently. Categorize your thoughts according to your preferences, view them at will and upgrade.</p>
            <p><a href="#" class="button-style">Read More</a></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>Exhibit Your Constructs</h3>
            <p>Sometimes you may feel the need to have other people judge your thoughts, comment on them and condone them. We allow you to that. Simply exhibit your thoughts to the world and the masses will be able to judge them. You can read other's thoughts and pick their brain or simply vote on them. Bookmark constructs of other Authors for future consideration.</p>
            <p><a href="#" class="button-style">Read More</a></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>Record Your Epiphanies, Brainwaves and Factoids</h3>
            <p>Who has time? We know that you do not. But then don't let that fleeting idea get away. Record an Epiphany or Brainwave and work upon it later.
              Some facts your brain is to occupied to store but you would like to record them. Create a Factoid and brush up upon them at will.</p>
            <p><a href="#" class="button-style">Read More</a></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>Research Options for Quick Searching</h3>
